examples.en: You're certainly in a playful mood!
She's an old dog, but she's still very playful.
She gave him a playful pinch.
He had a playful expression on his face.
He gave her cheek a playful squeeze.

Vanessa gave me a playful poke in the ribs.
The words play and playful are related.
